title: Just SOME of the signs I saw on a 30 minute walk through my neighborhood
text: The last one is mine! 🎃 I saw about twice as many, but you can only add 20 pictures. 🤣 Not a single sign for "the other guy" to be found.  I know that many of you live in red cities/counties/states, so here's a reminder that we're out here! 💙
